Package de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.message.m.serialize.bytebuffer

Integrity measurement byte buffer serialization interfaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ImReader<T extends ImData>
    Generic reader, that reads data from a byte buffer and parses it to an integrity measurement message object.
    ImWriter<T extends ImData>
    Generic writer, that accepts an integrity measurement message object and serializes it to the given byte buffer.
